sequenceDiagram
    actor U as You (in Claude)
    participant M as jetder-mcp
    participant J as Jetder API
    participant R as Registry (GHCR)
    U->>M: deployment-deploy (name, image, pullSecret?)
    Note over M: resolve project/location, validate image + pull-secret (no tokens)
    M->>J: deployment.deploy (Basic auth)
    J->>R: pull image (private uses pull-secret)
    R-->>J: image
    J-->>M: accepted
    M-->>U: success
    U->>M: deployment-get
    M->>J: read status + URL
    J-->>M: status=success, url
    M-->>U: live at https://your-app
